World Trade Averages for the Period 1998-2000

world_trade_avg_1998_to_2000.Rd

A matrix that summarises all the products that different countries exported to the rest of the world. This data uses the SITC revision 2 classification with four digits product codes. The unit is year 2000 USD.

world_trade_avg_1998_to_2000

Format

A sparse matrix with 226 rows and 785 columns.
